Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu... I failed you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:54.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew how you felt, but I pretended not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:57.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I lied to you even though you're my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's too late now,\Nbut I want you to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:08.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...about the day I let go of\NKureha's love, and why I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:14.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikumaaaaaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:15.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,"WHAT WE HOPE FOR"\N{\i1}Viens avec moi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Church chimes echo in the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:28.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offer up a prayer and betray today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:34.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wander in a dark forest, then become{\i0}\N{\i1}the morning moon at the Wall of Severance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:36.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't join the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.81,0:01:40.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I've made you stickier{\i0}\N{\i1}with sweet, thin honey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:44.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, approve me, I'll be a good girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:50.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Picture-book pages dancing on{\i0}\N{\i1}the breeze shake up shadowy memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:56.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting you-know-where,{\i0}\N{\i1}in an empty world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if everything falls apart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:14.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have to gracefully writhe,{\i0}\N{\i1}even if you have to bend space-time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flower petals will slowly{\i0}\N{\i1}enfold us on a starry night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:36.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}J'ai besoin de toi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:51.05,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"11 Years Ago・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:53.84,Main,,0,0,0,,She's done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she'd slow us down. Let's exclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:57.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Exclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:01.01,Main,,0,0,0,,--Exclude her.\N--Exclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I prepared myself that day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:09.40,Main,,0,0,0,,to die there all alone,\Nwithout anyone ever finding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:12.73,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay, you're not alone. I'm your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be together forever now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,My mom told me that as long as you don't\Nforget love, you'll never be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't give up on love,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:43.14,Main,,0,0,0,,even if you lose something,\Nyou'll never be invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:52.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to protect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:10.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:26.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha! Kureha! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:35.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forget love. I won't give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:36.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.65,Main,,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,...are friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:52.42,Main,,0,0,0,,And so Kureha and I became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,We shared so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:10.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Love was sweet, and kind, and made\Neverything seem to sparkle like a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:13.15,Main,,0,0,0,,So I got the wrong idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:17.36,Main,,0,0,0,,and thought the world had approved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,There's the traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard you're hanging out\Nwith a bear. Another girl saw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!\NMy mommy says bears are our enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:53.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears are evil! We gotta exclude them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:57.56,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true! We can be friends with bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna defend them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:00.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you're evil, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Exclude! Exclude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Exclude! Exclude! Exclude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hey guys, she's an evil girl who defends bears!\N--Exclude! Exclude! Exclude! Exclude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:14.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Exclude! Exclude! Exclude! Exclude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:31.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Exclude all traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:36.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl... Kureha got hurt for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:53.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Lick... lick...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:57.54,Main,,0,0,0,,This happened to her because I'm a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not okay for me to be a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:06.13,Main,,0,0,0,,If... If I were a human girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Could we be together forever?\NCould I protect Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:12.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Please tell me, Lady Kumaria!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:23.23,Main,,0,0,0,,My love's the real thing, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Court is in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Severance Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the land of enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:40.83,Main,,0,0,0,,for all living things...\Nyes, even human and bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us now pass judgment--\Nfor the sake of humans and bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.97,MainTop,,0,0,0,,LIFE Sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.18,MainTop,,0,0,0,,LIFE Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.01,MainTop,,0,0,0,,LIFE Beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:57.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this where Lady Kumaria lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Lady Kumaria has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:03.44,Main,,0,0,0,,She became meteors that\Nscattered across our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:07.70,Main,,0,0,0,,We now begin the Yuri Trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:11.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant-bear Ginko Yurishiro,\Nis there anything you wish to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:17.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be with Kureha forever!\NI want to protect Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,So please... make me a human girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:28.51,Main,,0,0,0,,However, there is one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:31.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You must relinquish love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:34.89,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, she will forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:38.56,Main,,0,0,0,,And you're not allowed to tell\Nanyone what happened here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:42.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's just like {\i1}The Little Mermaid{\i0}! Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:48.19,Main,,0,0,0,,When Kureha Tsubaki wakes up,\Nshe will most likely reject you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Reject?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:51.74,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,A-A bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.75,Main,,0,0,0,,S-Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:13.30,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, Lulu.\NTo get my wish to be a human girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:16.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I let go of Kureha's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:18.93,Main,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:24.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Someday, the time will come when\Nbears and people can be friends forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I was sent back to the bear world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:37.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yet you insist that you love this human girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:41.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't give up on love, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Dreadful... You are no longer a cub of Kumaria!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:51.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You are Ginko the Lone Wolfsbane,\Na blight on this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Begone, sinful child who betrays our Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:10:03.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You must wait. The time will come,\Nand you will find Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:08.32,Main,,0,0,0,,And, if you can make\Nfriends with her again... Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.32,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish will come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:15.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Exchange Promise Kisses with her.\NIf you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I can be a human girl, growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:23.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, defendant-bear Ginko Yurishiro, I ask you:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:28.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you become human?\NOr will you give up on love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:32.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't give up on love.\NI'll become human, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:44.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I waited for the time to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:54.53,Main,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:00.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I met you, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,"Incoming Call: Blocked Number"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:12.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It is, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,The Invisible Storm has begun. Now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:22.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't give up on love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:28.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't, either. I'll support your love, Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu, you always stayed by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You gave me love without\Nseeking anything in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:47.04,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine! I'll protect you, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:51.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go to the human world! Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:05.68,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"The Day They Transferred In・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,We hated you from the beginning--\Nand loved you from the beginning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:16.82,Main,,0,0,0,,And so I became a human girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:23.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, I wanted to become true\Nfriends with you. To cross the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:28.54,Main,,0,0,0,,She's here! She really does smell delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:34.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu... You were my true\Nfriend from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:48.81,Main,,0,0,0,,We all see the problem, agreed?\NWe must exclude the bear lurking in our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I assume everyone's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:56.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's confirm this one more time.\NWho should we use as bait for the bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's search sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.67,Main,,0,0,0,,"4. Saori Shimabukuro"\N"5. Hinako Serina"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:15.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"3. Aoi Uezu"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:18.17,Main,,0,0,0,,"2. Karen Tanaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:19.22,Main,,0,0,0,,"1. Evil = Kureha Tsubaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall I lick your wounds for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.69,Main,,0,0,0,,No, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're giving me the cold shoulder today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:50.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen to me: I want to eat Kureha Tsubaki.\NThat's a desire you and I share.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:53.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's find her and eat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I smell it, a delicious smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:14:00.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I smell a girl who won't back down on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious smell. Grr.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Grrrrrrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:17.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:23.11,Main,,0,0,0,,These girls need to learn that a hunter\Nis always in danger of being hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:53.23,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Bear-Killing Beam Truck.\NTarget Alpha sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:56.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Preparing to fire Eco-Kumagical Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:15:00.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Buzz buzz! Nasty nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:07.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Eco-Kumagical energy replenishing.\NWe'll be at full power in 10, 9, 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:13.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.26,Main,,0,0,0,,They really are beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:26.63,Main,,0,0,0,,To think she just walked\Nright in here after her bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,So, how did you tame her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:34.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you tell her you loved her,\Nmaybe give her a little kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:38.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmph! You way disgust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.15,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Bear-Killing Beam Truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:44.61,Main,,0,0,0,,We fired on Target Alpha and managed\Nto scratch her, but she got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:50.03,Main,,0,0,0,,This is D5. I've been informed\Nthat the door in the lily bed is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm heading there to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:57.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I was right, they're using that place\Nas their gateway. Wily bears...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:16:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, I have something good!\NI found {\i1}this {\i0}when I searched your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:03.67,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Your mom wrote it, right?\NA bear and a human, {\i1}friends{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:11.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Writing this crap is what\Ngot her killed by bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:17.89,Main,,0,0,0,,"Lady Kumaria"? Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,There are no gods in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:25.99,Main,,0,0,0,,The only thing ruling us is\Nthe invisible atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, bearie bearie bearie!\NI have your food right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:52.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That was close. When did they\Nget that tasteless weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go eat Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:17:02.23,Main,,0,0,0,,The desire to monopolize someone\Nis stronger than anything, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:05.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forget love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:13.24,Main,,0,0,0,,--Nasty...\N--We've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:14.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Nas... ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I've finally found true love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:25.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYou've already accepted me, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:32.22,Main,,0,0,0,,True love doesn't break in some stupid storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.05,Main,,0,0,0,,True love...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,...doesn't leave me all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:46.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I can hear her... Kureha's calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the same as back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:53.20,Main,,0,0,0,,When I got separated from the others,\NKureha was the only one to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:55.33,Main,,0,0,0,,She gave me love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,So this time, I'll be the one to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:17:59.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:07.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't do that. We're {\i1}bears{\i0}.\NYou can't tell me you've forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:12.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Because I'm your desire. Your love itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:16.26,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,True love...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.85,Main,,0,0,0,,...makes me leap into the storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:30.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to abandon me?\NThat's not possible! I'm your desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Beasts who lose their desire {\i1}die{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:50.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I will tear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,...myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.01,Main,,0,0,0,,...apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:58.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Silly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:13.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, I found you, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:27.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you even want at this point?\NIt's your fault this happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:35.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You were never my friend anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:40.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Humans and bears are severed!\NWe can't be together no matter what we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I know, growl. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:48.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become your friend again,\Nno matter how much you resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:52.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll become your friend,\Nand we'll do a Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Because if we do that, I can be human!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't forget love,\Nyou'll never be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.41,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't give up on love,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:04.16,Main,,0,0,0,,even if you lose something,\Nyou'll never be invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it! It's your fault\Neveryone died! Even Sumika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:16.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you... I won't forgive bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:21.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Go away. Go back to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:24.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I sent Yurigasaki back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:28.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Go, and never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:37.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,No... stay away... Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:46.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, I'll never back down on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:48.83,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:52.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, I'll never back down on my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:57.30,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to lose anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:33.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}... I came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Muahaha, you're a bad liar, Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu... Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:48.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin {\i0}let me escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,She said I wasn't her friend,\Nbut her lie was... super obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:22:04.82,Main,,0,0,0,,So I know she'll forgive you, Ginko.\NNo, she already has.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:06.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:13.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You can be her friend, Ginko.\NMake your love... come true, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You can get a Promise Kiss.\NI believe in you, Ginko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, I collected your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:30.77,Main,,0,0,0,,See? I'm so clever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:42.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.58,0:22:54.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the boundary that severed{\i0}\N{\i1}ripe moon from sleeping forest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.77,0:23:25.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break the law God shackles us with and smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:32.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned away from the bleating flock{\i0}\N{\i1}of shadows and howled my bloodthirsty ego{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here amidst the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.09,0:23:42.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Overflowing honey and soul{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to rend silk with my fangs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid you'll vanish{\i0}\N{\i1}like the world's last ray of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.97,0:23:59.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The savage beast inside me{\i0}\N{\i1}tore out the throat of innocence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:09.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, shoot me through the heart{\i0}\N{\i1}with your sweet-scented Barrett of love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:32.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant Kureha Tsubaki,\Ndo you admit your crime?
